        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You can induce a chemical reaction that allows a part of your body to glow. You must designate what part of your body glows when you take this feat.</p>\n<p>You begin to glow with bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for the next 20 feet. While you're glowing, you can't be @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Undetected] and you take a –4 penalty to Stealth checks to [[/act hide]] and [[/act sneak]]. You can Dismiss the glow as a free action. At 9th level, you shed bright light in a 40-foot radius and dim light for the next 40 feet.</p>"
        },
